name: Saldana
description:
Ethereum-based protocol that enables the reuse of ETH and Liquid Staking Tokens (LST) in the consensus layer, enhancing Ethereum’s staking infrastructure.
Our validator node in EigenLayer contributes to the network’s security and operation, allowing staked assets to be reused to validate and secure additional networks.
Saldana is a revolutionary team of crypto developers.
